HEADWORD: Riksdaler
<hw>Riks"da`ler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sw. See
<er>Rix-dollar</er>.]</ety> <def>A Swedish coin worth about twenty-seven
cents. It was formerly the unit of value in Sweden.</def>⟦br⟧
